description: Who’s in the mood for the frozen confections of your dreams? Well, thank goodness for Cruisin’ Creams; the old fashioned ice cream cart that’s sure to sweeten your heart. Embellish any event and delight your guests with this cream-ucopia of the best novelty treats we all grew up with and adore, like Good Humor, Klondike, Popsicle, and many more!If you’re craving quality ice cream and fantastic service, San Jose, you better be choosin’ Cruisin’ Creams.
name: Cruisin Creams Ice Cream Cart
